@startuml CLZ-MERO Product Search Activity

|User|
start
:Enter search keyword;

|Frontend|
:Send search request;

|Backend|
:Receive search query;
:Perform exact search\n(MongoDB regex);

if (Results found?) then (yes)
  :Return exact matches;
else (no)
  :Apply fuzzy search\n(Fuzzball algorithm);
  :Calculate similarity scores;
  :Merge and rank results;
  :Return fuzzy matches;
endif

|Frontend|
:Display results;

|User|
:View products;
stop

@enduml
